719633f-b.text:
(1)
Edgecombe Ave., west side, south from and including West 162nd Street, showing the Jumel Mansion (Roger Morris House) in the center of Roger Morris Park. Buildings on the right are on Jumel Terrace, west side, south from West 162nd to 160th Streets. Prominent apartment house, (left) is the Roger Morris, No. 400 West 160th Street at the S.W. corner of Edgecombe Ave.
October 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, from another angle.
October 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
A view showing the facade, which faces West 160th Street. Edgecombe
Ave. is on the right.
October 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
